metadata.name: Miss White Smoothie "Hunters" GESTURE #1
metadata.description: Ms. White Smoothie is one of the characters from the upcoming STS series. This is the genesis artwork that I've made from the STS girl series. The female character of STS has several skin color differences, so I want to unite the differences and support a diversity. I will raise themes about of nature, tech, lifestyle. mostly with colorfull style, semi abstract and destructive. I will give a clue of the names of the STS team. the first is Ms.White Smoothie's, the next is Ms.Black Jewely's & Ms. Red Killa's.
